As the pioneer of food delivery with The Pizza Company, Minor Food has enjoyed tremendous success and is currently the operator of 8 World-Class brands: The Pizza Company, Swensen’s, Sizzler, Dairy Queen, Burger King, The Coffee Club, Bonchon, and S&P.


We are proud to introduce “1112 Delivery" with the goal of exceeding our customers’ expectations. For the very first time, you can enjoy the convenience from Minor Food’s international brands all in one application. High quality food, delicious and hygienic meal delivery by our professional drivers. This service is available through the web, app, or dialing our call center, 1112.



Download the 1112delivery Mobile App now and enjoy mouth-watering food delivered to your door.
